Subject: [PATCH] drm/nouveau/svm: fail NOUVEAU_SVM_INIT ioctl on unsupported
 devices
Patch-mainline: v5.10.13
References: openEuler-21.03

stable inclusion
from stable-5.10.13
commit 112821f254b6f2d4a0f8e6a39f93cf0db62f95fb
